CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 5, 1961, page 11, reads: "Banquet Speaker - Thomas R. Ficklin, fourth from left, is shown addressing the Men's Unit of the Greater Pittsburgh Improvement League during its father and son banquet, held last Saturday at the East Liberty YMCA. Others are, left to right: Atty. Wendell Freeland, the Rev. LeRoy Patrick, the Rev. Charles L. Gordon, Mr. Ficklin, the Rev. Clarence E. McFadden and Arthur C. Holloway, GPIL president. An unidentified listener is seated in front. - Harris Photo"
TitMainTitle: Greater Pittsburgh Improvement League members Attorney Wendell Freeland, Rev. LeRoy Patrick, Rev. Charles L. Gordon, Thomas R. Ficklin, Rev. Clarence E. McFadden, and Arthur C. Holloway gathered around table for father and son banquet at East Liberty YMCA
